    {\displaystyle {\begin{aligned}y_{1}&=5x_{2}\\y_{2}&=4x_{1}^{2}-2\sin(x_{2}x_{3})\\y_{3}&=x_{2}x_{3}\end{aligned}}}
  is

  
    
      
        
          
            |
            
              
                
